  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "First listen and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "What was wrong with the man's story?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这个人的说法有什么问题？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "At the time the murder was committed, I was traveling on the 8 o'clock train to London, said the man.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“谋杀发生时，我正在开往伦敦的8点钟列车上。”那名男子说。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Do you always catch such an early train?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“你总是乘这么早的火车吗？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "asked the inspector.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "探长问道。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "Of course I do, answered the man.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“当然，”男子回答。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "I must be at work at 10 o'clock.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“我必须在10点钟到单位。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "My employer will confirm that I was there on time.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“我的雇主可以证明我准时到了。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "Would a later train get you to work on time?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“晚一点的火车能让你准时上班吗？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "asked the inspector.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "探长问。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "I suppose it would, but I never catch a later train.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“应该可以，不过我从不坐晚一点的火车。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "At what time did you arrive at the station?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“你几点到的车站？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "At 10 to 8, I bought a paper and waited for the train.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“7点50分。我买了份报纸，然后等车。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "And you didn't notice anything unusual?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“你没发现任何异常吗？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "Of course not.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“当然没有。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "I suggest, said the inspector, that you are not telling the truth.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“我认为，”探长说，“你没有说实话。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "text": "I suggest that you did not catch the 8 o'clock train, but that you caught the 8.25, which would still get you to work on time.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“我认为你没有乘8点钟的火车，而是乘了8点25分那班；那班车仍能让你准时上班。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "text": "You see, on the morning of the murder, the 8 o'clock train did not run at all.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“你看，谋杀发生的那个早晨，8点钟的列车根本没有运行。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "text": "It broke down at Fern Green station and was taken off the line.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“它在芬格林车站发生故障，被调离了线路。”"
      }
    }
  ],
